<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Services - AgriLinkHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Our Services</h1>
    <p>AgriLinkHub offers a comprehensive suite of services designed to support every aspect of the agricultural value chain.</p>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service">
        <h3>Marketplace Platform</h3>
        <p>A digital marketplace where farmers can list their products and buyers can discover fresh, local produce. Our platform ensures fair pricing and direct farmer-to-consumer connections.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <h3>Supply Chain Management</h3>
        <p>Streamline your supply chain with our tools for inventory management, order tracking, and logistics coordination. Reduce waste and improve efficiency.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <h3>Farming Resources</h3>
        <p>Access a wealth of knowledge including farming best practices, crop management tips, weather forecasts, and market price information.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <h3>Community Network</h3>
        <p>Connect with other farmers, share experiences, and learn from the community. Join forums, attend virtual events, and build valuable relationships.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <h3>Financial Services</h3>
        <p>Access financing options, insurance products, and payment solutions tailored for the agricultural sector.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service">
        <h3>Consultation & Support</h3>
        <p>Get expert advice on crop selection, pest management, sustainable farming practices, and business development.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>